    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The branch of science that is concerned with the study of energy and with the relationship of heat transfer and work to other forms of energy.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
